---
title: Caramelized Onion Burgers with Garlic Aioli and Baked Cauliflower 'Frites'
description: One of our favourites: the Caramelized Onion Burger – caramelized onions, spinach, soft brioche buns and homemade patties. Roasted cauliflower 'frites' and garlic aioli make the perfect sides.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-aux-oignons-caramelises-78b6da72.jpg
